name: Strangers in the Night
comments: Excellent from times to time, good song
Just love this song, Anita. So romantic.
'Scooby dooby do', still can't help singing that!!!!!!!!
Timeless charm from an enchanting voice.

"Something in my heart told me I must have you" ♥ 
Ageless song and voice.
Stg in my heart told me ...

The record player reminds me of my days in airforce. Listening to records is a different experience. I still listen to such golden tracks in my record player and compare the song with other formats. The hiss, the scratch,the statics add a dimension and nostalgia to the music.
It turned out so right, for strangers in the night.
He was so cool and what a singer.
